      • PropertiesInfo

        public PropertiesInfo(java.util.Properties props)
        Creates a simple implementation based on java's Properties. This implementation uses the reference to the properties passed. If you want a snapshot of these properties, you need to take a clone and pass the clone to the constructor.
        Parameters:
        props - The configuration store
